; Slice γ (2026-04-25) — Zazen meditation scaffold gains a single stone
; lantern (granite cylinder post + flat cap) modelled on the Garden roji
; lantern in ``godot_project/scenes/zones/Garden.tscn``. The motif gives
; the meditation locus a focal silhouette so that an agent in the zazen
; ERRE mode is visibly anchored to a contemplative landmark rather than
; standing on an empty plane. Dimensions match Garden's lantern (1.6 m
; post, 0.8 m cap) for visual consistency.

